norm_PLN

norm_PLN.Rd

Runs PLN function from the PLNmodels package and normalized the outputs

norm_PLN(Y)

Arguments

Y

count dataset

Value

  • MO Normalized means

  • SO Normalized marginal variances

  • sigma_obsVairance-covariance matrix Sigma as estimated by PLNmodels

Examples

 data=missing_from_scratch(n=100,p=10,r=1,type="scale-free", plot=TRUE)
norm_PLN(data$Y)
